{"tid":2307611,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本史上最高票房亞軍 取代《鐵達尼號》！","createTime":"2020-12-01T09:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T10:19:38.000Z","uid":386157,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a8f6f196981f0c4f88acfbb27ea84ed699bc36cc","tid":2307611,"uid":386157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"日本動畫電影《鬼滅之刃劇場版無限列車篇》氣勢如虹，在當地接連破紀錄，截至11月29日上映45天，票房衝破275億日圓（約20.3億港元），超越《鐵達尼號》保持多年不敗的262億日圓佳績，取而代之成為日本史上最高票房亞軍，下一步就是要挑戰動畫大師宮崎駿的《千與千尋》，以308億日圓保持了19年的冠軍紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n據報《鬼滅之刃》除了票房收逾275億日圓外，入場人次亦衝破2000萬，達到2053萬人次。事實上該片上映以來，已改寫多項紀錄，包括以10天便突破100億日圓票房、24天超過200億日圓、38天達到250億日圓的最快紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家喊嘅位喺邊度"},{"pid":"92866af003f9f25b5612bbf254e5f609c2a2cf32","tid":2307611,"uid":28580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:26:37.000Z","msg":"發夢返鄉下果段"},{"pid":"9deaac810c94fb112dfc7915d27ccb389d033df4","tid":2307611,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"千與千尋 呢D廢老野早應該收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ca4cd9c3b103eb016f8a47e99510ab5d30fffd","tid":2307611,"uid":71913,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:27:26.000Z","msg":"千與千尋找襲神作鬼滅<br />\n<br />\n一定會被拉落嚟 <br />\n<br />\n正義鬼滅必勝"},{"pid":"ec88b92b781d6f33beedffe7212c67bf493bfb29","tid":2307611,"uid":386157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9deaac810c94fb112dfc7915d27ccb389d033df4","tid":2307611,"uid":155818,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"千與千尋 呢D廢老野早應該收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T09:27:30.000Z","msg":"笑咗<img sr